{"tid":1663621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「學術交流」除警察憲委級外，有乜野政府位要特首先可以炒？","createTime":"2019-10-19T13:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T02:26:48.000Z","uid":257726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9459f5803db161d78596d394d8ff135af42473b6","tid":1663621,"uid":257726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:46:03.000Z","msg":"警務處處長、警務處副處長、警務處高級助理處長、警務處助理處長、總警司、高級警司及警司是香港警察職級中憲委級的職級，為高級警官（英文：Senior Officer）的級別。[1]憲委的意思為其委任必須刊登於《香港政府憲報》中，其任命及革除必須經由（香港主權移交前）香港總督／（香港主權移交後）行政長官同意。  <br />\n<br />\nFrom <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%81%B7%E7%B4%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E7%25B4%259A&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=fa8ecf3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%81%B7%E7%B4%9A</a>。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7899ce99c4282d4d139269a90bd7d59411dcb87","tid":1663621,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826b08603fcd6ad994d73c6c5a942e8782195bd4","tid":1663621,"uid":257726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}